       "state" : "closed",
       "body" : "**What does your Instant Answer do?** \r\nProvides translation of basic Greek phrases from English to Greek.\r\n\r\n\r\n**What problem does your Instant Answer solve (Why is it better than organic links)?**\r\nIt quickly provides the user with the information he has requested.\r\n\r\n\r\n**What is the data source for your Instant Answer? (Provide a link if possible)**\r\nOmniglot, http://www.omniglot.com/language/phrases/greek.php\r\n\r\n\r\n**Why did you choose this data source?**\r\nIt provides sufficient information on the searched topic.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Are there any other alternative (better) data sources?**\r\nAlternatives, yes. How good the alternatives are is somewhat subjective.\r\n\r\n\r\n**What are some example queries that trigger this Instant Answer?** \r\n\"greek phrases\", \"english to greek\", \"basic greek phrases\", \"basic greek\"\r\n\r\n\r\n**Which communities will this Instant Answer be especially useful for? (gamers, book lovers, etc)**\r\nGenerally for all knowledge seekers, especially travellers, tourists and foreign language enthusiasts.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Is this Instant Answer connected to a DuckDuckHack [Instant Answer idea](https://duck.co/ideas)?**It is an IA cheat sheet.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Which existing Instant Answers will this one supercede/overlap with?**\r\nNone at this moment.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Are you having any problems? Do you need our help with anything?**\r\nNo, but we are confident we can rely on the DDG community when we come across difficulties.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Where did you hear about DuckDuckHack? (For first time contributors)**\r\nBy searching in the DDG community.\r\n\r\n\r\n**What does the Instant Answer look like? (Provide a screenshot for new or updated Instant Answers)**\r\n![fist success1](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/15343142/10794501/da871040-7d9d-11e5-90c2-c0e20a7b57db.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\nPlease place an 'X' where appropriate.\r\n\r\n```\r\n- [X] Added metadata and attribution information (https://duck.co/duckduckhack/metadata)\r\n- [X] Wrote test file and added to t/ directory (https://duck.co/duckduckhack/goodie_tests)\r\n- [X] Verified that instant answer adheres to design guidelines (https://duck.co/duckduckhack/design_styleguide)\r\n- [X] Verified that instant answer adheres to code styleguide (https://duck.co/duckduckhack/code_styleguide)\r\n- [X] Tested cross-browser compatibility\r\n\r\n    Please let us know which browsers/devices you've tested on:\r\n    - Windows 10\r\n        - [X] Google Chrome\r\n        - [X] Firefox\r\n        - [] Opera\r\n        - [] IE 11\r\n        - [] Microsoft edge\r\n        \r\n    - Windows 8\r\n        - [X] Google Chrome\r\n        - [X] Firefox\r\n        - [] Opera\r\n        - [] IE 10\r\n\r\n    - Windows 7\r\n        - [X] Google Chrome\r\n        - [X] Firefox\r\n        - [] Opera\r\n        - [] IE 8\r\n        - [] IE 9\r\n        - [] IE 10\r\n\r\n    - Windows XP\r\n        - [] IE 7\r\n        - [] IE 8\r\n\r\n    - Linux\r\n        - [X] Google Chrome\r\n        - [X] Firefox\r\n        \r\n    - Mac OSX\r\n        - [] Google Chrome\r\n        - [] Firefox\r\n        - [] Opera\r\n        - [] Safari\r\n\r\n    - iOS (iPhone)\r\n        - [] Safari Mobile\r\n        - [] Google Chrome\r\n        - [] Opera\r\n\r\n    - iOS (iPad)\r\n        - [] Safari Mobile\r\n        - [] Google Chrome\r\n        - [] Opera\r\n\r\n    - Android\r\n        - [X] Firefox\r\n        - [X] Native Browser\r\n        - [X] Google Chrome\r\n        - [] Opera\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n-----\r\nIA Page: https://duck.co/ia/view/greek_cheat_sheet",
